name: ANZA Technology Network
tag_list: technology, business-matching, mentoring, market-entry, globalization, investment, capital-raising, high-growth-business
overview:
ANZA Technology Network is a business accelerator that works with Australian, New Zealand, American and Asian entrepreneurs to access new markets and commercialize globally. The ANZA network consists of more than 5,000 industry professionals, primarily in the United States and China who can make valuable connections for tech entrepreneurs that lead to capital raising, collaborative partnerships and new customers.

ANZA has assisted hundreds of companies since its inception in 2002. Services include market research, business matching and a “fast track” program to accelerate new market traction. Programs can be customized to suit each companies’ specific needs.
